title: Season End Date ???
body: So what date will the ranked queue be disabled for the up-coming patch ( season 6 )

replies.body:
Season 5 ended on 11/11. It is currently preseason.

Season 6 will not start until mid-late January. My guess is January 15th.

I think Riot are trying to set specific dates from now on so everything is clear. 15/1 start of season, 11/11 end of season for the past 3 years.
"My tears have all dried up, kid"
